dcterms:description: A dataset for Math Word Problems (MWP) that consists of chain-of-thought data generated by the code-davinci-002 model from OpenAI, with original questions sourced from the GSM8K dataset and enhanced by prepending four in-context examples to each question.
dcterms:title: Math Word Problems (MWP)

dcterms:description: A novel compilation of 11.6k Chinese PET/CT report-impression pairs from real clinical data, focusing on determining whether patients have pancreatic cancer and whether there is distant metastasis.
dcterms:title: cPET-11K
